  <brief_title>Study of Pembrolizumab in Combination With Ublituximab and TGR-1202 in Patients With Relapsed-refractory CLL or Richter's Transformation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase I/II Study of Pembrolizumab in Combination With TG-1101 (Ublituximab) and TGR-1202 in Patients With Relapsed-refractory Chronic Lymphocytic Leukemia (CLL) or Richter's Transformation (RT)</official_title>
