  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety and effectiveness of pembrolizumab in
      combination with ublituximab and TGR-1202, in patients with advanced CLL or Richter's
      Transformation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
